    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Method ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            228,
            651,
            286,
            678
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Based onspin-weighted SCNNs (Esteves etal,NeurlP'20).   \n·Phase collapse activation: $x _ { 0 }  W _ { 1 } x _ { 0 } + W _ { 2 } | x | + b$ Inspired byGuth et al,arXiv'21. Efficient spin-weighted spherical harmonics on TPUs $^ \\circ$ Avoid tensor slicing/concatenation. $\\mathrm { o }$ Use DFTmatrices instead of FFT. ",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            721,
            243,
            843
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "·Spectral batch normalization,pooling and residual connection. ",
        "bbox": [
            47,
            848,
            251,
            863
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
