    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "·Takeasetofatmospheric variables like temperature,wind,humidity,and predict their futurevalues with fully convolutionalmodels.   \n·WeatherBench (Rasp et al):predict directly3or5daysahead.   \n·Keisler(arXiv'22):predict iteratively in 6h increments. Ourlargestmodel:256x256x78inputsand outputs;iterated for12steps during training,upto20during inference. ",
        "bbox": [
            516,
            661,
            762,
            782
